{"tid":640693,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得名校仔好撚戇鳩","createTime":"2018-04-24T12:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T16:50:56.000Z","uid":99568,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d2c85eb31defd9be09e5664faccf1418f963835c","tid":640693,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:37:19.000Z","msg":"條撚樣 都係 過咗去英國讀嘅, 佢就成日係咁話自己以前間學校 個 籃球 校隊 全港第一, 又係咁話自己係名校入面 做大佬, 成日打到人哋仆街, 仲要扮曬霸氣咁樣, 帶埋曬啲 rolex 約埋曬啲off-white以為自己好撚型, 仲要以為自己好撚靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ， 因為佢係 籃球撚, 成日 無啦啦喺度 原地射三分, 有時又喺canteen 做 post move<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個重點就係原來佢淨係讀過嗰間名校 兩年, 中二畢業之後就已經去咗英國, 但係佢嘅口吻好似講到 自己係 大師兄咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d611608d33f693d0c1e9b3a56e8c191508f6b0","tid":640693,"uid":99568,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:39:14.000Z","msg":"唔係妒忌佢有錢, 但係佢 18歲人就 帶埋曬啲rolex 又喺度用gucci皮帶， 仲要成日喺度曬命 話自己 屋企有幾多對錶, 成個大陸土豪咁樣, 同支那人有咩分別？"},{"pid":"0116c9b325539c3d8a2ebb5efe631239fe7bc6e9","tid":640693,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:40:57.000Z","msg":"條撚樣仲要以為自己英文好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又話自己間名校 英文 點好點好點好法， 但係其實自己啲英文口音 啲香港口音重撚到仆街"},{"pid":"6cd740260fc3654499d127b9bd7676a0540d0be6","tid":640693,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:41:47.000Z","msg":"讀名校嘅係咪覺得自己有光環，好有優越感?"},{"pid":"71bb8f78e1e76ce0f8539b28ddfdfb5ec0de1072","tid":640693,"uid":5460,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:42:49.000Z","msg":"覺<br />\n支持你用個 keyboard / 電話車鳩佢"},{"pid":"eceb6c177942b0ff3ad08cdb1de433381056df46","tid":640693,"uid":164730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:42:51.000Z","msg":"英華定大Hihi? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a262f1e6bab98c49ada2fbf97de5632376f56dc","tid":640693,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:44:57.000Z","msg":"佢嘅戇鳩特質 簡直就十項全能<br />\n<br />\n1） 曬命有錢土豪<br />\n2)   自以為靚仔<br />\n3） 籃球L, 成日無啦啦 扮curry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4)   講英文扮曬有外國口音, 但係其實 聾   嘅都知佢唔係<br />\n，<br />\n5） 以為自己好撚大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a51d9d161b4f314971d7bb2627ada01f5447d4","tid":640693,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eceb6c177942b0ff3ad08cdb1de433381056df46","tid":640693,"uid":164730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:42:51.000Z","msg":"英華定大Hihi? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:45:16.000Z","msg":"咁都畀你估到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad96e53d426dd2250d9d5460b55b4a0bd3cf1fc0","tid":640693,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79a51d9d161b4f314971d7bb2627ada01f5447d4","tid":640693,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eceb6c177942b0ff3ad08cdb1de433381056df46","tid":640693,"uid":164730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:42:51.000Z","msg":"英華定大Hihi? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:45:16.000Z","msg":"咁都畀你估到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:45:29